BattleshipBot
=====================================

BattleshipBot will suggest you where to shoot while playing Battleship War. Written in CoffeeScript.

Usage:

var bot = new BattleshipBot

bot.suggest() // will return a Point[x, y] with the highest probability of hit

bot.update(x, y, command) // to provide information to Bot (eg: 3, 7, ["miss", "hit", "carrier", "battleship", "submarine", "destroyer" or "patrol"])

Calculations and probailities based on "The Linear Theory of Battleship" by The Virtuosi.
